  mso-no-proof:yes'>Argon is an inert yellow gas.<o:p></o:p></span></p>
  <p class=3DMsoNormal><span lang=3DEN-GB style=3D'mso-ansi-language:EN-GB;
  mso-no-proof:yes'>It is typically used in weapons, shielding and reactor
  components. Argon is found at Gas Giant and Frozen Gas Giant worlds and G=
as
  clouds.<o:p></o:p></span></p>
